# Commit messages

- **Format**: Always use [Conventional Commits](https://www.conventionalcommits.org/).
- **Language**: Write the commit message in **English** (title and body).

## Examples

```
feat(ui): add piggy GIF to login screen
fix(sheets): handle empty CSV without crashing
docs: update Telegram bot setup guide
chore(deps): bump vite to 7.3.1
```

When suggesting a commit message for the user, output it in this format and in English only.
